WEBVTT

00:08.102 --> 00:09.323
Whoa!

00:09.324 --> 00:11.397
No, no.
Is that...

00:11.398 --> 00:12.577
Our friend
the drug dealer.

00:12.578 --> 00:13.583
At least it used to be.

00:13.584 --> 00:15.246
No. No, no, no.
I didn't see that.

00:15.247 --> 00:16.539
I-I <i>don't</i> see that.

00:16.540 --> 00:18.671
You mean him?
There's no "him."

00:18.672 --> 00:20.239
Sure there is...
Well, what's left of him.

00:20.240 --> 00:21.210
He's right there.

00:21.211 --> 00:23.546
You can't...
Okay, he's not...

00:23.547 --> 00:25.548
You can't kill people
in a sound stage...

00:25.549 --> 00:27.050
<i>My</i> sound stage!

00:27.051 --> 00:28.465
You rented it to me.

00:28.466 --> 00:30.583
You said
it wasn't illegal!

00:30.584 --> 00:32.305
I'm not a part of this.
Julian.

00:32.305 --> 00:35.141
There's a dead guy
in my sound stage!

00:35.142 --> 00:36.767
Julian, he's not dead.
He's just...

00:36.768 --> 00:39.312
Well, I guess
he <i>could</i> be dead by now.

00:39.313 --> 00:41.778
I can't go to prison, okay?
You said it yourself.

00:41.779 --> 00:42.774
They'll <i>like</i> me there.

00:42.775 --> 00:44.150
You're not going
to prison.

00:44.151 --> 00:45.442
- I have a family, man!
- Nobody is going to prison.

00:45.443 --> 00:46.944
Will you just calm down?!

00:46.945 --> 00:51.304
Besides, we're the only two
people that know about this.

00:52.823 --> 00:54.774
Is that guy dead?

00:54.775 --> 00:57.227
Okay, <i>three</i> people know.

00:57.228 --> 00:59.278
Four, counting Haley.

00:59.279 --> 01:01.748
We're going to jail.

01:04.418 --> 01:08.338
Rise and shine!

01:08.339 --> 01:10.840
Hey, look.

01:10.841 --> 01:13.596
Front page.

01:13.597 --> 01:15.178
Not your best photo, true,

01:15.179 --> 01:17.058
but still,
front page is good, no?

01:19.132 --> 01:21.437
Before I get large cash,

01:21.438 --> 01:23.019
I have to show
in good faith

01:23.020 --> 01:25.905
that you are still alive
and somewhat well.

01:25.906 --> 01:27.306
Okay.

01:27.307 --> 01:30.321
Open your eyes,
chin up.

01:30.322 --> 01:32.698
Say "the cheese."

01:34.952 --> 01:38.496
Would you like 8x10
or wallet size?

01:40.225 --> 01:41.621
No?

01:41.622 --> 01:43.540
Nathan Scott.

01:43.541 --> 01:47.004
The rest is silence.

01:47.005 --> 01:48.256
No.

01:48.257 --> 01:49.507
Please.

01:50.735 --> 01:52.802
Not the hood.

02:00.107 --> 02:03.760
Because you say "please."

02:03.761 --> 02:05.728
Etiquette counts,
my friend.

02:12.203 --> 02:13.906
Look at this marmaduke.

02:13.907 --> 02:16.155
He... he crazy dog.

